OL,3,CFamilies of Nottingham attack victims
OL,4,Cwelcome decision to review homicide law
OL,6,FThe Law Commission announced on Friday
OL,7,F6 December that it had accepted a
OL,8,Frequest by Lord Chancellor Shabana
OL,9,FMahmood to review homicide law.
OL,11,FSpecifically, the commission will look
OL,12,Finto how homicide is categorised and
OL,13,Fthe impact of diminished
OL,14,Fresponsibility.
OL,16,F'Flawed and archaic'
OL,18,FIn a joint statement, the families of
OL,19,Fthe three victims killed by Calocane
OL,20,Fsaid they welcomed the review.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
