OL,6,F"Our laws, practices and processes are
OL,7,Ffailing," they said.
OL,9,F"The are flawed and archaic. Because
OL,10,Fof this, a gross miscarriage of
OL,11,Fjustice has been served and Valdo
OL,12,FCalocane has been able to manipulate
OL,13,Fthe system to avoid punishment for his
OL,14,Fheinous crimes.
OL,16,F"We have never disputed his illness;
OL,17,Fhowever it is clear that he knew
OL,18,Fexactly what he was doing, he knew
OL,19,Fthat what he was doing was wrong, and
OL,20,Fhe chose to do it anyway.
