OL,6,F"As such, he is now a patient within
OL,7,Four medical system with no current
OL,8,Fprocess to serve any punishment for
OL,9,Fhis crimes.
OL,11,F"Had our laws changed, as was first
OL,12,Fproposed almost 20 years ago, this
OL,13,Foutcome would have been very
OL,14,Fdifferent."
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country,
OL,17,FBarnaby's mother Emma Webber said she
OL,18,Fwanted to be involved in the review.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@KO]
