OL,6,F"Our homicide laws and our sentencing
OL,7,Fneeds to be urgently reviewed, because
OL,8,Fthey are out of date, they are
OL,9,Farchaic," she said.
OL,11,F"As a society, we have moved on.
OL,12,FCrimes have moved on, but sadly the
OL,13,Flaw hasn't. I always quote the then
OL,14,FMinister for Justice Alex Chalk that
OL,15,F'just because it's the law, doesn't
OL,16,Fmean it's right, and just because it's
OL,17,Fthe law, it doesn't mean it shouldn't
OL,18,Fchange'.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
