OL,6,F"I think that's proof today that it
OL,7,Fneeds to and it must, and we will be
OL,8,Flobbying very hard to make sure that
OL,9,Fwe are involved - if we can be - from
OL,10,Fthe victims' perspective, but it must
OL,11,Fchange."
OL,13,FAs part of its review, the Law
OL,14,FCommission will examine an 18-year-old
OL,15,Freport on homicide law.
