OL,6,FIt has been almost 20 years since the
OL,7,Foriginal report, and the Law
OL,8,FCommission themselves have suggested
OL,9,Fthat they would want to look again at
OL,10,Ftheir recommendations before
OL,11,Fsuggesting that the Government should
OL,12,Fadopt them now," Mr Davies-Jones wrote.
OL,14,F"The problems identified in the 2006
OL,15,Freport have remained largely
OL,16,Funchanged, particularly with regard to
OL,17,Fhow diminished responsibility should
OL,18,Fbe reflected in the classification of
OL,19,Fhomicide offences.
