OL,6,F"However, as society and the law has
OL,7,Fmoved on, new problems and possible
OL,8,Flimitations have emerged, including
OL,9,Fthe operation of the law of joint
OL,10,Fenterprise and the extent to which the
OL,11,Flaw reflects a modern understanding of
OL,12,Fthe effects of domestic abuse."
